ChangeHistory.Change: Original Release - needs MMTs
Add prompts an updated. Added MMTs. Some MMTs are missing pending creation by GM
Added all the GM Fault codes
Worked on adding repair lines and adding connector ID on fault description
Updating MMTs and repair instructions
Increased timeout of VoltageRange tests to 10sec from 300msec. Adjusted lower limits based on first LT6 run-through.
Adjusted lower limits of knock sensors and changed bias state to P from H.
Removed G403 test. Using B3 Ch31 as N-Bias to ground vehicle. Also validates G403
Updated Notes for B3 Ch31 N Bias
Added No Bias for B3 Ch31 after N-Bias use is done
Adjusted Fuel Rail Pressure Sensor lower limit to 3V from 4V. (LT6/LT7 only)
Increased upper limit of Generator (LT6/LT7) from 3V to 7V.
O2 WRAF Sensor and Intake Manifold Tuning Valve testing updates for LT6.
Changed channel of WRAF Sensor
changed lower limit from 5V to 3V for Left Front Acc. sensor (FE2,FE4,FE6,FE7)
Removed "2022" RPO from Brake Pad wear 1/2
Changed test description of Ride Height Sensors to Magentic Ride (MR) Sensor
Removed Placeholder test Bd6 Ch14
Updated terminology of WRAF to Pre O2 Sensors for LT6
Changed lower limit of MAF (LT6) from 4 to 2.5V
added ground to vehicle via tester. Moved G175 test to board 3.
Adjusted Limits for LT2
Reversed circuit polarity of crank shafts and cam shaft position sensors for LT2.
Adjusted Limit for Throttle Body LT2
Changed knock sensor test to Square Wave LT2 only
Adjusted PWM for Knock Sensors LT2
Adjusted RMS PWM on knock sensors LT2
adjusted voltage limits for knock sensors LT2
Adjusted voltage limits on knock sensors LT2
Updated test repair instructions for Oxygen O2 Wide Range Air Fuel Sensor 1
Changed O2 descriptions LT2
changed pwm for knock sensor to 50%Duty cycle
changed lower limit for knock sensor to 0.3 volts from 0.4
changed lower limit of second konc sensor from 0.4 to 0.3 volts
lowered both konck sensors down to 0.26 volts
updated the Board for control of the PIP Relays
removed text from repair instructions that have pictures
Added missing repair instruction photos
Added more missing repair instruction pictures for LT2
updated connector time out to 600 seconds
changes limits on b1ch10 from 5 to 2

Changed limits on B3ch16 ground G175 from 5-8v to 2-6v 
changed lower limit on B1ch6 MAF from 5 to 2.5v
raised limit on g175 bto 8v
ADDED LT6 ENGINE COOL TEMP SENSOR PIC AND CAM POSITION SENSOR PIC
Added test for exaust flapper valve by P biasing B1ch25 and reading on B1 ch24 and ch26   2.5v to 8v range for both
changed upper limit to exaust flapper valve from 8v to 12v
changed exhaust valve descriptions, added ID, added picture for electronic throttlebody motor

optioned ##OUT## 3/4 brakepad sensor,
widened range on engine oil control solenoid B6Ch16 lower from 5v to 0.5v
double checking save location
changed B1c25 from P to H bias exhaust flapper valves
Optioned out B1 Ch24 and 26
##OUT option code added to Engine Oil COntrol Solenoid B6ch16
set lower limit on b1 ch 24 and 26 to -1v
Changed H-bias to P-bias for exhaust flapper valves B1 ch 25
Changed B1 ch25 to P-bias, changed ch24 and 26 to 0.4v lower limit
Changed desctriptions of exhaust valves
added pictures to B1 ch24 and 26 exhust valves
Added Group to double check all test connectors are indeed connected. Plant stated instances of connectors being disconnected prior to the latches being locked.
Moved connector double check to after draw down.
